'''Józef Wojciechowski''' (born January 17, 1947) is a Polish developer, owner of J.W. Construction Holding S.A., and former owner of [[Polonia Warsaw]] football club. He is the 31st richest Pole as of 2013, with his wealth estimated at 950 millions Polish [[zloty|zloties]], or about 300 million dollars.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://100najbogatszych.wprost.pl/obiekt/id,1764/ide,30/idk,0/edycja-2013-Jozef-Wojciechowski.html |title=Józef Wojciechowski - Ranking 100 Najbogatszych Polaków - edycja 2013 |publisher=100najbogatszych.wprost.pl |date= |accessdate=2013-10-24}}</ref>

